{"title":"挽肖华","authors":["舒同"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":8,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽肖华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年英武咤风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举义破关尔先行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征路上同饮马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沂蒙山巅共挥旄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年浩劫遭冤狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正气凛然妖魔惊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜见红日照春晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西山举杯论旧情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吟诗讴歌留佳作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建政立规见丹心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊悉沉疴夺君去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥泪成诗慰英灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八五年八月十六日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}